title: Sony - DSC-W830 20.1-Megapixel Digital Camera - Silver
description: This Sony DSC-W800 digital camera's 20.1-megapixel, 1/2.3 Super HAD CCD sensor enables you to shoot stunning photographs and 720p video footage. The 2.7 Clear Photo LCD lets you view stored content.

components.title: 20.1-megapixel, 1.7 Super HAD CCD sensor
components.detail: Captures high-resolution images up to 5152 x 2896 pixels.

components.title: 8x optical/up to 32x digital/up to 256x total zoom
components.detail: Through a Carl Zeiss Vario-Tessar lens for precise zooming and accuracy.

components.title: 2.7' LCD
components.detail: Provides a clear view, so you can easily compose and review your shots.

components.title: High-definition movie mode
components.detail: Allows you to record smooth, detailed video clips in 720p resolution.

components.title: Optical SteadyShot image stabilization
components.detail: With Active mode reduces image blur caused by camera shake and vibration, so you can take crisp, steady shots. ISO up to 3200 for improved image capture in low-light conditions.

components.title: Scene modes
components.detail: Include high sensitivity, soft snap, soft skin, landscape, night portrait, night scene, gourmet, beach, snow, fireworks and pet to accommodate various shooting scenarios. Sweep Panorama mode lets you capture expansive landscapes.

components.title: Memory Card Compatibility
components.detail: Memory Stick PRO Duo, Memory Stick Micro, microSD, Secure Digital, Secure Digital Extended Capacity (SDXC), Secure Digital High Capacity (SDHC)

title: Canon - PowerShot ELPH 180 20.0-Megapixel Digital Camera - Silver
description: The high-sensitivity CMOS sensor and DIGIC 4+ image processor of this Canon PowerShot SX530 HS digital camera combine to form the HS SYSTEM, which helps enhance quality in low-light conditions, so you can capture the shot you want, wherever you are.

components.title: 1/2.3 CMOS sensor
components.detail: Captures high-resolution images up to 4608 x 3456 pixels.

components.title: 50x optical/4x digital/200x total zoom
components.detail: Delivers the versatility needed to capture your subjects, whether they are nearby or far away

components.title: 3' LCD
components.detail: With a screen resolution of 461,000 dots allows you to easily frame subjects and view information, even from a wide angle.

components.title: 1080p Full HD video
components.detail: Helps you capture the moment as it unfolds. A dedicated movie button makes it easy to shoot video.

components.title: DIGIC 4+ image processor
components.detail: Combines with the CMOS sensor to form the Canon HS SYSTEM, which delivers a high level of quality in low light.

components.title: Intelligent IS
components.detail: Reduces image blur caused by camera shake and vibration

components.title: Scene modes
components.detail: Include portrait, smart shutter, burst, snow and fireworks for simple adjustment. Creative Shot mode uses the original composition, color and lighting to add a touch of artistic flair.

title: Sony - Cyber-shot DSC-HX80 18.2-Megapixel Digital Camera
description: Keep your phone on the side, and let this Sony Cyber-shot digital camera do the work. It enjoys a 18.2-megapixel sensor and an 30x zoom so that you can focus on the action and get highly detailed shots. Powerful flash modes and solid low-light performance means this Sony Cyber-shot digital camera gets the results you want.

components.title: 18.2-megapixel Exmor R® CMOS
components.detail: Captures high-resolution images up to 4896 x 3672 pixels.

components.title: 30x optical/60x digital zoom
components.detail: Get super close and clear with the premium ZEISS® Vario-Sonnar T* lens from wide angle (24mm equivalent).

components.title: 3' color Xtra Fine LCD multi-angule display
components.detail: Easily frame for selfies or to shoot objects like pets at eye-level without having to get down on the ground.

components.title: Retractable OLED Tru-Finder™ viewfinder
components.detail: The electronic viewfinder faithfully displays what will appear in your recording, including the effects of your camera settings, so you can accurately monitor the results.

components.title: Movie Recording Mode
components.detail: Capture 50Mbps Full HD (1920x1080) 60p high quality video with minimal compression noise even in scenes with a lot of movement.

components.title: BIONZ® X image processor.
components.detail: This brings out the full resolving power of professional lens to deliver high resolution, and stunning low-light sensitivity with improved image clarity and reduced grain for both stills and movie

components.title: 5-axis Optical SteadyShot™ image stabilizer
components.detail: Advanced technology reduce blur caused by camera shake when shooting movies, allowing you to move along with the action, and get clear images of your subject in motion, even when zoomed in.

components.title: Memory Stick Duo, Memory Stick PRO Duo, Memory Stick PRO-HG Duo, Secure Digital, Secure Digital Extended Capacity (SDXC), Secure Digital High Capacity (SDHC)
